%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%2C%20mornings%20are%20both%20exciting%20and%20restful.%20Sip%20on%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20(or%20many%20of%20them)%20as%20you%20relish%20your%20spread%20of%20breakfast.%20The%20stillness%20is%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20birds.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%20session%20of%20tennis%20on%20the%20court%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350504%2Fmarble-palace-kolkata-museum-tour-first-private-zoo-raja-rajendra-mullick-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20around%20the%20palace%20gardens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20sitting%20by%20the%20ponds%20and%20listening%20to%20the%20music%20that%20drifts%20from%20one%20of%20the%20live%20band%20shows%20put%20up%20for%20the%20guests%2C%20serenity%20is%20in%20the%20details.%20Naturally%2C%20the%20guests%20who%20come%20to%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20from%20around%20the%20world%20find%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20take%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20place%20back%20with%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20royal%20residence%20reflects%20Bengali%20style%20interspersed%20with%20colonial%20architecture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-6-1726574226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%