%20a%20double%20ton%20in%20this%20match.%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%2C%2026%2C%20said%20he%20has%20spoken%20to%20his%20brother%20who%20is%20seven%20years%20younger%20to%20the%20man%20who%20is%20once%20again%20knocking%20on%20the%20national%20selectors'%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20him.%20He%20is%20fine%20but%20will%20take%20two-three%20months%20to%20recover%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarfaraz%2C%20who%20struck%20a%20half-century%20against%20England%20in%20the%20Dharamsala%20Test%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20became%20the%20first%20player%20to%20score%20an%20Irani%20Cup%20double%20hundred%20for%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%2015th%20first-class%20century%20will%20certainly%20dispel%20all%20doubts%20about%20his%20slot%20as%20a%20reserve%20middle-order%20batter%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20Test%20season%20(8%20games).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20penchant%20for%20making%20big%20scores%2C%20Sarfaraz%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20known%20to%20play%20big%20knocks.%20I%20feel%20good%20doing%20things%20I'm%20known%20for.%20Mumbai%20also%20needed%20me%20to%20bat%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20win%20the%20Irani%20Cup%20after%20a%20long%20time.%20Back%20of%20the%20mind%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20playing%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20putting%20as%20many%20runs%20on%20the%20board%20as%20possible%20which%20will%20help%20the%20team%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ekana%20Stadium%20track%20had%20underlying%20moisture%20on%20the%20second%20day%20and%20the%20dampness%20contributed%20to%20the%20ball%20seaming%20around%20initially%20and%20the%20extra%20bounce%20made%20it%20challenging%20for%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz's%20driving%20on%20the%20off-side%20was%20regal%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20add%20to%20his%20footwork%20against%20spinners.%20He%20was%20brutal%2C%20especially%20against%20left-arm%20spinner%20Manav%20Suthar%20(0%2F137%20in%2037%20overs)%2C%20who%20looked%20clueless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20he%20employed%20the%20negative%20leg-stump%20line%20and%20Sarfaraz%20would%20either%20slightly%20go%20inside%20out%20or%20bent%20down%20on%20one%20knee%20to%20slog%20sweep%20it%20for%20maximums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20further%20about%20his%20monumental%20effort%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20played%20in%20the%20Irani%20Cup%20earlier%20and%20scored%20a%20century%20for%20the%20Rest%20of%20India.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20innings%20for%20me%20as%20I'm%20playing%20for%20my%20home%20team.%20I%20am%20putting%20an%20extra%20effort%20so%20that%20Mumbai%20can%20lift%20the%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20weather%20was%20obviously%20a%20challenge.%20We%20are%20up%20against%20some%20of%20best%20players%20in%20India%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20them%20have%20played%20international%20cricket.%20I%20was%20looking%20to%20make%20runs%20against%20them.%20It%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20my%20best.%20I%20am%20satisfied%20with%20the%20time%20I%20spent%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20bunch%20has%20put%20in%20lot%20of%20effort%20to%20reach%20the%20Irani%20Cup%20by%20winning%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20last%20season.%20It's%20not%20like%20our%20team%20can't%20win%20this%20tournament).%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20are%20one%20of%20the%20best%20teams%20in%20India.%20So%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20do%20well%20and%20win%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728015420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fn1phsb8_sarfaraz-x_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt