e%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20banner%20flew%20over%20the%20Hudson%20River%20and%20circled%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%2C%20a%20global%20symbol%20of%20human%20dignity%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201971%20genocide%2C%20as%20documented%20by%20US%20Congress%20Resolution%20HR%201430%20in%202022%2C%20claimed%202.8%20million%20lives%20and%20saw%20at%20least%20200%2C000%20predominantly%20Hindu%20women%20raped%2C%20leaving%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Bangladesh's%20Hindu%20population%20has%20dwindled%20from%2020%20per%20cent%20in%201971%20to%20just%208.9%20per%20cent%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20of%20targeted%20violence%2C%20systematic%20impoverishment%2C%20lynchings%2C%20kidnappings%20of%20minor%20girls%2C%20and%20forced%20job%20resignations%20affecting%20up%20to%20200%2C000%20Hindus%2C%20along%20with%20property%20seizures%2C%20pose%20a%20serious%20existential%20threat%20to%20the%2013%20to%2015%20million%20Hindus%20living%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20August%205%2C%202024%2C%20there%20have%20been%20around%20250%20verified%20attacks%20and%20over%201%2C000%20reported%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitangshu%20Guha%2C%20from%20the%20Bangladesh%20Hindu%20Community%20and%20one%20of%20the%20event%20organisers%2C%20highlighted%20the%20threat%20and%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BHindus%20in%20Bangladesh%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20will%20raise%20awareness%20among%20the%20civilised%20world%20and%20prompt%20the%20UN%20to%20take%20action%20to%20save%20the%20victims%20of%20militant%20Islamic%20forces%20in%20Bangladesh.%20If%20Bangladesh%20becomes%20Hindu-free%2C%20it%20will%20become%20Afghanistan%202.0%2C%20and%20militants%20will%20spread%20to%20neighbouring%20India%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20including%20the%20West.%20This%20is%20everyone's%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Mehta%2C%20another%20activist%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Interfaith%20Human%20Rights%20Coalition%20who%20helped%20organise%20the%20event%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20time%20for%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20to%20put%20aside%20politics%20and%20officially%20recognise%20the%201971%20Bangladesh%20genocide%2C%20the%20largest%20genocide%20since%20World%20War%20II.%20Three%20US-based%20organisations--The%20Lemkin%20Institute%20for%20Genocide%20Prevention%2C%20Genocide%20Watch%2C%20and%20the%20International%20Coalition%20of%20Sites%20of%20Conscience--have%20already%20recognised%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20Pakistani%20occupation%20forces%20and%20their%20Islamist%20allies%20in%201971%20as%20genocide%2C%20primarily%20targeting%20the%20Hindu%20minority.%20The%20UN%20must%20follow%20suit%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20another%20looming%20genocide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjit%20Chowdhary%2C%20founding%20member%20of%20Sree%20Gita%20Sangha%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20US%2C%20urged%20the%20Bangladesh%20government%20to%20stop%20all%20violence%20against%20the%20Hindu%20community%20and%20address%20political%20differences%20through%20democratic%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Islamist%20fundamentalism%20in%20Bangladesh%20poses%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20India%2C%20as%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20spread%20through%20porous%20borders%2C%20affecting%20West%20Bengal%20and%20beyond%2C%20with%20existing%20ties%20between%20radical%20forces%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20raising%20concerns%20among%20mainstream%20Americans%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20anxieties%20seen%20during%20the%20Afghanistan%20crisis.%20Humanitarian%20watchdogs%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20worsening%20conditions%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20fearing%20that%20escalating%20violence%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20full-scale%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20are%20being%20urged%20to%20boycott%20Bangladeshi%20garments%2C%20which%20account%20for%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20export%20earnings%2C%20until%20the%20violence%20ceases%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plea%20has%20been%20made%20to%20executives%20of%20major%20buyers%20of%20Bangladeshi%20garments--such%20as%20Walmart%2C%20H%26amp%3BM%2C%20Gap%20Inc.%2C%20Target%2C%20PVH%20Corp%2C%20and%20VF%20Corporation--to%20halt%20shipments%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20as%20economic%20support%20for%20the%20country%20today%20is%20seen%20as%20enabling%20terrorism%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jewish%20community%20in%20America%20has%20also%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Hindu%20minority%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20to%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Israel.%20Just%20as%20the%20world%20rallied%20against%20extremist%20violence%20in%20Israel%2C%20many%20are%20now%20calling%20for%20immediate%20intervention%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20prevent%20further%20atrocities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20live-streamed%20on%20StopHinduGenocide.org%2C%20where%20all%20atrocities%20are%20being%20methodically%20documented%2C%20along%20with%20historical%20context%20and%20the%20ominous%20future%20facing%20Bangladesh's%20Hindus%20unless%20the%20global%20community%20takes%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728010980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvf5bl6oo_stop-violence-on-bangladesh-hindus-banner-twitter_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fairline-banner-over-new-york-city-calls-to-stop-violence-on-bangladesh-hindus-6712103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20powerful%20appeal%20to%20the%20global%20community%2C%20Hindu%20American%20groups%20flew%20a%20massive%20airline%20banner%2C%20calling%20for%20urgent%20global%20action%20to%20stop%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%2