stroyed%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERainfall%20collected%20by%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20weather%20stations%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20near%20Asheville%2C%20reached%20their%20highest-ever%203-day%20totals%20during%20the%20event%2C%20ranging%20from%20nearly%2013%20inches%20to%20over%2031%20inches%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclimate.ncsu.edu%2Fblog%2F2024%2F09%2Frapid-reaction-historic-flooding-follows-helene-in-western-nc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20North%20Carolina%20State%20Climate%20Office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227054%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20flooded%20street%20in%20Asheville%2C%20NC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd9e2d7de5c8fd4834c5c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeavy%20rains%20from%20Hurricane%20Helene%20caused%20flooding%20across%20western%20North%20Carolina%2C%20like%20here%20in%20Asheville.%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Sue%20Gerrits%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20only%20about%202.6%25%20of%20the%204.3%20million%20properties%20across%20the%20state%20%E2%80%94%20or%20around%20115%2C000%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20had%20flood%20insurance%20as%20of%20June%202024%2C%20according%20to%20private%20provider%20Neptune%20Flood%20Insurance%2C%20which%20analyzed%20data%20from%20the%20government-backed%20National%20Flood%20Insurance%20Program.%20And%20that's%20a%202.5%25%20year-over-year%20coverage%20decrease%20from%20June%202023%2C%20Neptune%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina%20Department%20of%20Insurance%20communications%20director%20Jason%20Tyson%20estimated%20that%20about%20139%2C000%20properties%20in%20the%20state%20have%20flood%20insurance%20through%20the%20NFIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20estimate%20includes%20private%20flood%20insurance.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20private%20flood%20insurance%20policies%20in%20the%20US%20is%20small%20compared%20to%20the%20amount%20of%20NFIP%20policies%2C%20according%20to%20a%202023%20report%20from%20independent%20insurance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.policygenius.com%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fprivate-flood-insurance-vs-nfip%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMost%2520policies%2520are%2520provided%2520and%2Cand%2520availability%2520of%2520additional%2520coverages.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovider%20PolicyGenius%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Carolina%20Joint%20Information%20Center%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20still%20too%20early%20to%20provide%20estimates%20on%20the%20number%20of%20buildings%20damaged%20or%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20destroyed%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fda04c5ccfc192a552b3a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20home%20destroyed%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene%20in%20Black%20Mountain%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ESue%20Gerrits%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20disaster%20assistance%20does%20help%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20homes%20with%20mortgage%20payments%2C%20home%20loans%2C%20or%20bill%20payments.%20But%20without%20flood%20insurance%2C%20many%20homeowners%20may%20be%20left%20with%20a%20significant%20financial%20burden.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20problem%20with%20flood%20insurance%20is%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20regular%20home%20insurance%20covers%20flooding%2C%20which%20is%20rarely%20the%20case%2C%20four%20experts%20knowledgable%20about%20flood%20insurance%20and%20disaster%20management%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20just%20think%20that%2C%20'Oh%2C%20yeah%2C%20I%20have%20insurance.%20I%20have%20homeowner's%20insurance.%20I%20have%20State%20Farm%20or%20whatever.%20That%20must%20cover%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Trevor%20Burgess%2C%20the%20President%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Neptune%20Flood%20Insurance%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20doesn't.%20They%20have%20to%20buy%20a%20separate%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20influencing%20why%20so%20few%20people%20have%20flood%20insurance%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20required%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20only%20homes%20and%20businesses%20with%20government-backed%20mortgages%20in%20areas%20that%20are%20designated%20high-risk%20flood%20zones%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.floodsmart.gov%2Fam-i-required-have-flood-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegally%20required%20to%20have%20flood%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20drivers%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20people%20get%20flood%20insurance%20is%20whether%20or%20not%20they're%20required%20to%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffrey%20Schlegelmilch%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20and%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Disaster%20Preparedness%20(NCDP)%20at%20Columbia%20Climate%20School%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20don't%20live%20in%20one%20of%20these%20areas%2C%20one%20of%20these%20floodplains%20that%20trigger%20that%2C%20then%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20just%20simply%20don't%20get%20flood%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlegelmilch%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMargaret%20Walls%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Climate%20Risks%20and%20Resilience%20Program%20at%20nonprofit%20research%20institute%20Resources%20for%20the%20Future%2C%20said%20that%20people%20also%20wrongly%20believe%20that%20if%20they're%20not%20in%20a%20high-risk%20flood%20area%2C%20then%20they're%20not%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20homes%20that%20are%20in%20those%20designated%20floodplains%20relative%20to%20the%20total%20number%20of%20homes%2C%20but%20there's%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20flood%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20Walls%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20issues%20in%20the%20flood%20world%20is%20that%20the%20mapped%20areas%20where%20FEMA%20says%20you're%20supposed%20to%20have%20flood%20insurance%20policy%20are%20not%20the%20areas%20that%20are%20all%20risky.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20areas%20where%20you're%20at%20risk%20outside%20of%20those%20mapped%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalls%20explained%20that%20people%20don't%20understand%20their%20actual%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20think%20that%20the%20map%20is%20telling%20them%20their%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20Walls%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20not.%20It's%20just%20telling%20them%20where%20they%20have%20to%20have%20a%20mandatory%20purchase%20of%20a%20flood%20insurance%20policy.%20But%20it's%20not%20saying%20that%20you're%20zero%20risk%20when%20you're%20outside%20of%20that%20area.%20And%20as%20climate%20changes%20happening%2C%20those%20risks%20are%20going%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20areas%20devastated%20by%20flooding%20in%20western%20North%20Carolina%20were%20largely%20not%20considered%20to%20be%20high-risk%20flood%20areas.%20The%20State%20of%20North%20Carolina's%20Flood%20Risk%20Information%20System%20designates%20many%20of%20the%20counties%20in%20the%20region%20that%20were%20most%20affected%20by%20flooding%20after%20Helene%20as%20%26quot%3Bminimal%20flood%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflood.nc.gov%2Fncflood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20map%20on%20their%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20almost%20always%20associate%20flood%20risk%20with%20hurricanes%20and%20coastal%20storm%20surge%20in%20Florida%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20and%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeremy%20Porter%2C%20who%20leads%20climate%20implication%20research%20at%20First%20Street%2C%20a%20public-benefit%20corporation%20that%20evaluates%20climate%20risk%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fclimate-change-hurricane-helene-flooding-north-carolina-f49b2a6bf2b549473e0211f883332592%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20think%20of%20western%20North%20Carolina%20and%20the%20Appalachian%20mountains%20as%20an%20area%20that%20has%20significant%20flood%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20perception%20that%20a%20certain%20place%20is%20safe%20from%20flooding%20contributes%20to%20the%20problem%2C%20Schlegelmilch%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20those%20things%20we%20look%20at%20areas%20like%20Asheville%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20that%20were%20thought%20of%20as%20climate%20havens%2C%20where%20people%20thought%2C%20'Well%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20escape%20the%20worst%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20move%20there%2C'%26quot%3B%20Schlegelmilch%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20unfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20just%20an%20important%20reminder%20that%20we%20cannot%20outrun%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20insurance%20to%20protect%20your%20home%20and%20mitigate%20your%20financial%20risks%20is%20an%20important%20step%2C%20and%20more%20people%20need%20to%20take%20that%20precaution%2C%20Schlegelmilch%20said%2C%20a%20sentiment%20that%20Walls%20and%20Burgess%20also%20echoed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYanjun%20Liao%2C%20an%20economist%20and%20fellow%20at%20Resources%20for%20the%20Future%2C%20added%20that%20people%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20even%20unexpected%20flood%20events%2C%20like%20what%20happened%20in%20western%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20think%20that%20a%20lot%20more%20people%20need%20flood%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20Liao%20said.%20%26quot%3BOftentimes%20even%20people%20who%20are%20living%20outside%20of%20the%20flood%20zones%2C%20the%20100-year%20flood%20zones%20and%20sometimes%20outside%20500-year%20flood%20zones%2C%20can%20face%20these%20kind%20of%20unexpected%20flood%20damage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiao%20said%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20flood%20insurance%20can%20be%20burdensome%2C%20particularly%20for%20those%20who%20live%20in%20more%20disaster-prone%20areas.%20But%20the%20alternative%20may%20be%20even%20more%20costly%3A%20rebuilding%20after%20a%20devastating%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-north-carolina-flood-insurance-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728004772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fda3105ccfc192a552b525%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-north-carolina-flood-insurance-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Helene's%20heavy%20rains%20devastated%20western%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20few%20properties%20had%20flood%20insurance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1415%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-north-carolina-flood-insurance-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Melania%20Trump%20is%20latest%20Republican%20First%20Lady%20to%20back%20abortion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728004472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Feaa1%2Flive%2Fcb053530-818e-11ef-98f4-8f408a3dba7c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce3zxk9w955o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%20apparent%20support%20of%20abortion%20access%20puts%20her%20at%20odds%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20has%20taken%20credit%20for%20helping%20to%20overturn%20Roe%20v%20Wade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A827%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce3zxk9w955o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce3zxk9w955o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.c