misunderstandings%2C%20especially%20for%20new%20joiners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-left-google-after-3-years-career-dead-end-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJerry%20Lee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%2029%2C%20a%20former%20manager%20at%20Google%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Wonsulting%2C%20a%20career%20consulting%20company.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20education%20and%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20got%20the%20idea%20of%20making%20a%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20from%20an%20old%20supervisor%20I%20worked%20for%20when%20I%20joined%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20then-manager%20told%20me%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20problems%20teams%20face%20is%20a%20clash%20of%20working%20styles%20among%20their%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20putting%20together%20a%20list%20containing%20one's%20working%20style%20and%20preferences%20to%20minimize%20such%20clashes.%20The%20list%20can%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20managers%20and%20colleagues%20to%20set%20the%20right%20expectations%20upfront.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20his%20suggestion%20and%20decided%20to%20make%20my%20own%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20based%20on%20my%20manager's%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Google%2C%20there%20is%20an%20internal%20employee%20database%20where%20you%20can%20write%20a%20short%20description%20about%20yourself.%20I%20decided%20to%20put%20up%20my%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20there%20so%20that%20anyone%20could%20look%20it%20up%20when%20they%20looked%20me%20up%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22344ea394-cd31-4463-821a-32821b850c5b%5C%22%3EHaving%20a%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20is%20helpful%20for%20both%20individual%20contributors%20and%20managers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20is%20helpful%20even%20as%20an%20individual%20contributor.%20It%20allows%20me%20to%20set%20the%20terms%20of%20how%20I%20would%20like%20to%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20point%20of%20friction%20that%20I%20see%20teams%20face%20is%20that%20they%20just%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20with%20each%20other%2C%20especially%20when%20someone%20new%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20such%20a%20document%20lays%20out%20how%20you%20like%20to%20receive%20feedback%2C%20how%20you%20like%20to%20work%2C%20and%20the%20type%20of%20communicator%20you%20are.%20It%20also%20helps%20to%20minimize%20friction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20these%20things%20upfront%20will%20help%20align%20expectations%20within%20a%20team%20from%20the%20very%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jerry%20Lee's%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f12a22cfb7f307e573cbeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20included%20a%20link%20to%20his%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20on%20his%20profile%20in%20Google's%20employee%20database.%20This%20was%20so%20that%20his%20coworkers%20could%20take%20a%20look%20at%20it%20when%20they%20looked%20him%20up.%3Cp%3EJerry%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20shared%20my%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20with%20my%20Google%20coworkers%2C%20I%20received%20two%20types%20of%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20type%20of%20feedback%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20more%20common%2C%20is%20that%20people%20were%20appreciative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20wow%2C%20that's%20really%20cool.%20I%20appreciate%20you%20sharing%20how%20you%20operate%20upfront.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20type%20of%20feedback%20%E2%80%94%20they%20just%20said%20thanks%2C%20and%20didn't%20read%20the%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20I%20haven't%20received%20any%20criticism%20for%20sharing%20such%20a%20document.%20But%20I%20would%20be%20taken%20aback%20if%20that%20happened%20since%20I'm%20just%20sharing%20how%20I%20like%20to%20operate%2C%20hoping%20it%20reduces%20friction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20prefer%20to%20share%20their%20working%20styles%20more%20casually%2C%20like%20in%20a%20one-on-one%20introductory%20meeting.%20While%20that%20is%20the%20default%20way%20for%20people%20to%20communicate%20their%20working%20preferences%2C%20it%20only%20helps%20you%20understand%20people%20from%20a%20higher%2C%20broader%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20actually%20working%20with%20them%2C%20I%20think%20people%20would%20appreciate%20getting%20to%20know%20the%20minutiae%20of%20their%20colleagues'%20working%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20also%20shared%20this%20document%20on%20social%20media%20and%20received%20mixed%20responses.%20One%20group%20wants%20to%20use%20it%20in%20their%20own%20teams%2C%20and%20another%20group%20calls%20me%20a%20%26quot%3Btry-hard%26quot%3B%20for%20doing%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I'd%20rather%20over-communicate%20than%20under-communicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dc5836d-55a6-42e6-8749-8dfba3b87c42%5C%22%3ENot%20every%20industry%20may%20welcome%20it%2C%20but%20having%20a%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20is%20still%20good%20for%20self-reflection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jerry%20Lee%20in%20a%20black%20blazer%20and%20white%20T-shirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64de553fb698ac0019db6d5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221292%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20said%20there%20are%20benefits%20to%20making%20your%20own%20%26quot%3BWorking%20With%26quot%3B%20manual%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20intend%20to%20share%20it%