ected%2C%20the%20trick%20to%20putting%20a%20thinking%20person%20onto%20a%20cruise%20ship%20was%20just%20finding%20a%20bunch%20of%20other%20thinking%20people%20to%20take%20the%20cruise%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%243%2C000%20cost%20of%20the%20transatlantic%20cruise%2C%20plus%20the%20workshop%20fee%2C%20felt%20like%20money%20well%20spent.%20I%20ate%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-avoid-free-time-dining-cruises-frequent-traveler-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20swing%20dancing%2C%20watched%20some%20talented%20performers%2C%20drank%20a%20lot%20of%20wine%2C%20and%20generally%20lived%20it%20up%2C%20age%2040-style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOkay%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20mentally%20apologized%20to%20my%20spouse%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20might%20be%20having%20a%20bit%20of%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292f86328-ed77-41dd-9d13-f0c554c169ec%5C%22%3EBack%20on%20land%2C%20I%20started%20questioning%20my%20career%20choices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20difficulty%2C%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20came%20when%20I%20got%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20thought%20that%20the%20writing%20retreat%20would%20scratch%20my%20creative%20itch%2C%20and%20I'd%20return%20home%20to%20my%20regular%20career%20as%20a%20government%20contractor%20and%20keep%20writing%20on%20weekends.%20Instead%2C%20I%20had%20a%20full-blown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmidlife-crisis-real-americans-experience-intense-job-strain-earnings-years-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emidlife%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20hell%20am%20I%20doing%20with%20my%20life%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%2C%20as%20I%20stared%20at%20yet%20another%20spreadsheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20really%20want%20a%20practical%20career%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20questioned%2C%20as%20I%20read%20through%20a%20pile%20of%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20a%20mid