%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661803351caec1275a6f24ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20federal%20court%20once%20again%20blocked%20Biden%20from%20carrying%20out%20broader%20student-loan%20forgiveness.%20%3Cp%3EKyle%20Mazza%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20federal%20court%20in%20Missouri%20placed%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20on%20Biden's%20broader%20student-debt%20relief%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20ruling%20officially%20blocks%20the%20relief%20from%20being%20implemented%20pending%20a%20final%20legal%20decision%20from%20the%20court.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20decision%20came%20on%20the%20same%20day%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20on%20the%20relief%20was%20set%20to%20expire.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20whiplash%20continues%20for%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Judge%20Matthew%20Schelp%20of%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Missouri%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20by%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20placed%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20on%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20plan%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20under%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20ruling%20came%20just%20hours%20after%20it%20appeared%20a%20separate%20federal%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-broader-debt-relief-case-transfer-missouri-biden-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emay%20have%20granted%20borrowers%20a%20lifeline%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20a%20group%20of%20GOP%20state%20attorneys%20general%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20Georgia%20in%20September%20to%20block%20the%20debt%20relief%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20ruled%20that%20Georgia%20was%20the%20improper%20venue%20for%20the%20lawsuit%20and%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20Missouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchelp's%20ruling%20comes%20on%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20relief's%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20%E2%80%94%20had%20Schelp%20not%20moved%20ahead%20and%20placed%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20on%20the%20relief%2C%20the%20restraining%20order%20would%20have%20expired%2C%20and%20Biden%20would%20have%20been%20permitted%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20implementing%20the%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBalancing%20the%20harm%20and%20the%20injury%2C%20merged%20with%20the%20public's%20interest%2C%20easily%20leads%20this%20Court%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20preliminary%20injunctive%20relief%20should%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Schelp%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.moed.215155%2Fgov.uscourts.moed.215155.57.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20public%20has%20an%20immense%20interest%20in%20its%20own%20government%20following%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20also%20wrote%20that%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20is%20necessary%2C%20as%20it%20will%20preserve%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20prevent%20the%20administration%20from%20canceling%20student%20debt%20pending%20a%20final%20legal%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20had%20previously%20intended%20to%20begin%20canceling%20student%20debt%20in%20October%2C%20and%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20post%20the%20final%20rule%20for%20the%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20from%20the%20GOP%20attorneys%20general%20argued%20that%2C%20according%20to%20internal%20documents%20they%20obtained%20on%20communications%20between%20the%20department%20and%20servicers%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20was%20preparing%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%20which%20they%20said%20violated%20administrative%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20latest%20ruling%2C%20Schelp%20wrote%20that%20the%20Education%20Department%20is%20enjoined%20from%20%26quot%3Bmass%20canceling%20student%20loans%2C%20forgiving%20any%20principal%20or%20interest%2C%20not%20charging%20borrowers%20accrued%20interest%2C%20or%20further%20implementing%20any%20other%20actions%20under%20the%20Rule%20or%20instructing%20federal%20contractors%20to%20take%20such%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20development%20in%20the%20legal%20roller%20coaster%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20have%20been%20on%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Along%20with%20the%20lawsuits%20to%20block%20Biden's%20broader%20debt%20relief%2C%20his%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20is%20also%20blocked%20in%20court%20pending%20a%20final%20legal%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20the%20administration%20will%20pursue%20other%20forms%20of%20relief%20for%20borrowers%20as%20the%20legal%20process%20progresses.%20An%20Education%20Department%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20earlier%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20relief%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-biden-debt-cancellation-education-department-relief-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727994774000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ff110da7031864927f63a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-biden-debt-cancellation-education-department-relief-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20hours%20after%20the%20lawsuit%20to%20block%20broader%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20was%20transferred%20to%20Missouri%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20blocked%20the%20relief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A103%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-biden-debt-cancellation-education-department-relief-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%