ways%20had%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-watch-pga-championship-golf-live-stream-weekend-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etournament%20streaming%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20television.%20Despite%20his%20best%20efforts%20to%20educate%20me%2C%20I%20couldn't%20care%20less%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20par%20and%20a%20birdie.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20I%20could%20focus%20on%20was%20how%20seemingly%20boring%20the%20sport%20was.%20I%20couldn't%20understand%20why%20anyone%20would%20willingly%20spend%20hours%20chasing%20a%20tiny%20ball%20from%20hole%20to%20hole.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELittle%20did%20I%20know%20the%20sport%20would%20become%20a%20cornerstone%20for%20my%20marriage%20and%20mental%20health%20decades%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208439d55-0193-4adb-8db0-870c8bfa182e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20time%2C%20golf%20became%20a%20way%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20to%20reconnect%20and%20spend%20time%20together%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20to%20my%20dismay%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20and%20married%20a%20golf%20lover.%20For%20years%2C%20he%20asked%20if%20I'd%20try%20it%2C%20and%20I%20always%20told%20him%20to%20have%20fun%20without%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20we%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20inside%20and%20outdoor%20activities%20were%20limited%2C%20my%20husband%20suggested%20golf%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20was%20framed%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20while%20keeping%20our%20distance%20from%20others.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20still%20didn't%20understand%20the%20appeal%20but%20I%20reluctantly%20agreed%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20because%20I%20was%20going%20stir-crazy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20quickly%20turned%20into%20something%20more%20meaningful.%20The%20rounds%20at%20the%20club%20were%20hours%20spent%20without%20distractions%20and%20screens%20(except%20for%20a%20few%20breaks%20for%20the%20necessary%20Instagram%20shots)%20%E2%80%94%20just%20us%2C%20nature%2C%20and%20the%20game.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20a%20shared%20interest%20that%20wasn't%20watching%20Netflix%20created%20a%20space%20for%20us%20to%20grow%20closer.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20found%20that%20playing%20golf%20together%20felt%20like%20a%20form%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-went-to-marriage-therapy-to-prepare-for-birth-child-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecouples%20therapy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20gave%20us%20time%20and%20space%20to%20talk%2C%20laugh%2C%20and%20support%20each%20other%20through%20the%20game's%20inevitable%20challenges.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EPlus%2C%20I%20loved%20our%20post-golf%20dinners%20overlooking%20the%20beautiful%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20isn't%20to%20say%20there%20isn't%20still%20heated%20banter%20when%20he%20shouts%20%26quot%3BMore%20left!%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20cart%20as%20I'm%20swinging%20%E2%80%94%20but%20no%20relationship%20is%20perfect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c4d4c74-da36-47ac-a777-831ccef0e2d1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sport%20also%20helped%20me%20struggle%20less%20with%20perfectionism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Sara%20Iannacone%20and%20her%20husband%20smiling%20together%20on%20a%20golf%20course%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2d71ad17aa3c7b2b56a8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20can%20spend%20hours%20golfing.%20%3Cp%3ESara%20Iannacone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20my%20forray%20into%20golf%20wasn't%20all%20sunny.%20In%20the%20early%20days%20of%20playing%20I%20nearly%20let%20my%20lifelong%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperfectionism-toxic-definition-anxiety-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estruggles%20with%20perfectionism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20take%20over.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20initial%20focus%20was%20hitting%20the%20perfect%20shot%20every%20time.%20When%20things%20didn't%20go%20as%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20which%20happened%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20let%20that%20frustration%20carry%20into%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spent%20rounds%20mumbling%20expletives%20after%20over-swinging%20or%20slicing%20the%20ball%2C%20and%20I'd%20impatiently%20pace%20when%20we%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20group%20ahead%20of%20us.%20I%20considered%20the%20day%20a%20failure%20if%20I%20wasn't%20hitting%20consistent%20shots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20time%20and%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ehelp%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Finterpersonal-therapy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etherapy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20worrying%20about%20the%20perfect%20shot%20was%20wasting%20precious%20time.%20From%20there%2C%20%3Cspan%3EI%20worked%20hard%20to%20shift%20my%20mindset.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20berating%20myself%20for%20a%20poor%20shot%2C%20I%20laughed%20at%20the%20mishits%20and%20savored%20the%20good%20ones.%20Rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20my%20game%2C%20I%20cherished%20having%20a%20shared%20experience%20with%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20wasn't%20easy%2C%20but%20golf%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20enjoy%20moments%20for%20what%20they%20are%20%E2%80%94%20not%20how%20perfectly%20they%20play%20out.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20I%20happily%20putz%20along%2C%20content%20if%20I%20hit%20the%20ball%20in%20the%20intended%20direction.%20I%20enjoy%20the%20soft%20breeze%20and%20sun%20on%20my%20skin%20while%20waiting%20for%20our%20turn%20to%20tee%20off%20on%20a%20slow%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20anyone%20resisting%20trying%20something%20new%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20it's%20something%20your%20partner%20enjoys%20%E2%80%94%20I%20encourage%20you%20to%20give%20it%20a%20shot%20(no%20golf%20pun%20intended).%20You%20might%20be%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20it%20can%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-test-bids-deeper-relationships-friendships-gottman-institute-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeepen%20your%20connection%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20provide%20unexpected%20benefits%20for%20your%20own%20well-being.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-golfing-improved-marriage-mental-health-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727988002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2d750ce3009a0fac8dff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-golfing-improved-marriage-mental-health-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20hated%20golf%20for%20years%20but%20finally%20went%20with%20my%20husband.%20It's%20been%20great%20for%20our%20marriage%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20ditch%20toxic%20perfectionist%20tendencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sara%20Iannacone%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-golfing-improved-marriage-mental-health-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20October%20Prime%20Day%3A%20How%20to%20earn%20up%20to%2010%25%20back%20on%20your%20A