com%2Firan-used-one-of-most-advanced-missiles-massive-israel-attack-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran%20claimed%20it%20launched%20the%20Fattah%20missile%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20has%20described%20this%20weapon%20as%20hypersonic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-used-one-of-most-advanced-missiles-massive-israel-attack-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Chairs%20Urgent%20Top-Level%20Security%20Meet%20On%20Widening%20West%20Asia%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20the%20government's%20topmost%20decision-making%20body%20-%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%20over%20the%20crisis%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20comprising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Adviser%2C%20discussed%20in%20detail%20the%20fresh%20hostilities%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20the%20sharp%20escalation%20after%20Iran's%20ballistic%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20recent%20developments%20in%20West%20Asia%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerning%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20highest%20committee%20in%20the%20country%20delved%20upon%20various%20issues%20arising%20from%20the%20ongoing%20and%20widening%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20several%20key%20issues%2C%20they%20discussed%20the%20impact%20on%20trade%2C%20navigation%2C%20and%20supply%20chains%20-%20especially%20the%20supply%20of%20oil%2C%20petroleum%2C%20and%20its%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20urged%20all%20parties%20involved%20in%20the%20conflict%20to%20address%20all%20issues%20urgently%2C%20and%20through%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20%26quot%3Bmust%20not%20take%20a%20wider%20regional%20dimension.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIMPACT%20ON%20MARITIME%20TRADE%20AND%20SUPPLY%20CHAINS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20conflict%20doesn't%20just%20affect%20those%20who%20are%20party%20to%20it%2C%20but%20has%20a%20fallout%20that%20impacts%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20region%20and%20even%20the%20world.%20With%20the%20sharp%20escalation%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%2C%20India%20is%20bracing%20for%20wider%20trade%20disruptions%20across%20the%20key%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20can%20lead%20to%20significantly%20higher%20cargo%20freight%20tariffs%20as%20Lebanon's%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20militants%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen%2C%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20most%20attacks%20on%20merchant%20ships%20and%20vessels%20carrying%20cargo%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Sea%20crisis%20began%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20when%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20militia%20disrupted%20global%20trade%20in%20the%20area.%20For%20India%20alone%2C%20it%20affected%20petroleum%20exports%20which%20dropped%2037.56%20per%20cent%20to%20%245.96%20billion%20in%20August%20this%20year%2C%20down%20from%20%249.54%20billion%20in%20the%20same%20month%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Sea%20route%20followed%20by%20the%20Suez%20Canal%20accounts%20for%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20exports%20-%20worth%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20crore%2C%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20imports%2C%20worth%20Rs%2017%20lakh%20crore%2C%20as%20per%20data%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20overall%20merchandise%20trade%20(exports%20and%20imports%20combined)%20in%20FY23%20was%20Rs%2094%20lakh%20crore%2C%20with%2068%20per%20cent%20(in%20value%20terms)%20and%2095%20per%20cent%20(in%20volume%20terms)%20shipped%20by%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20trades%20heavily%20with%20the%20Gulf%20nations.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20government%20data%2C%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20or%20GCC%20now%20contributes%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20total%20trade%2C%20and%20sectors%20like%20energy%2C%20defence%2C%20security%2C%20and%20health%20are%20growing%20rapidly%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20countries%20reached%20%24162%20billion%20last%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727985720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F305fcd14_pm-modi-cabinet-committee-on-security-meet-ani_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-chairs-urgent-top-level-security-meet-on-widening-west-asia-crisis-6710175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20the%20government's%20topmost%20decision-making%20body%20-%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%20over%20the%20crisis%20in%20West%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-chairs-urgent-top-level-security-meet-on-widening-west-asia-crisis-6710175%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Surgery%20gone%20wrong%3A%20Priyanka%E2%80%99s%20honest%20confession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727985463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113918448%2Cimgsize-45968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsurgery-gone-wrong-when-priyanka-chopras-honest-confession-on-her-botched-nose-surgery-reminded-of-its-consequences%2Farticleshow%2F113918457.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%