%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20and%20an%20alleged%20confidant%20of%20its%20former%20principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20Ashish%20Pande%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20corruption%20case%20it%20is%20investigating%20alongside%20the%20horrific%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20young%20doctor%20that%20had%20shocked%20the%20country.%20Officials%20of%20the%20Central%20agency%20claimed%20Ashish%20Pande%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20is%20associated%20with%20its%20student%20wing.%20%C2%A0There%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20no%20confirmation%20or%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fifth%20arrest%20in%20the%20corruption%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20agency%20had%20arrested%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20and%20three%20others%20--%20his%20bodyguard%20Afsar%20Ali%2C%20Suman%20Hazra%20and%20Biplab%20Sinha%2C%20vendors%20supplying%20medical%20equipment%20to%20the%20hospital%20when%20Ghosh%20was%20the%20principal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Pandey%2C%20who%20is%20also%20employed%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20is%20reportedly%20associated%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Students'%20Wing%20-%20TMCP.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20the%20TMCP%20unit%20president%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20Chhatra%20Parishad%20(students'%20unit)%20state%20president%20and%20party%20spokesperson%20Trinankur%20Bhattacharya%20told%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20yet%20to%20hear%20details%20about%20the%20case.%20But%20as%20of%20now%2C%20we%20can%20say%20that%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20own%20course%20and%20we%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20justice%20system.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Pandey%20was%20earlier%20mentioned%20in%20the%20list%20of%2059%20people%20at%20the%20hospital%20who%20were%20issued%20show-cause%20notices%20by%20the%20hospital%20administration%20and%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20an%20inquiry%20committee%20set%20up%20after%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20second%20year%20post-graduate%20student.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Pandey%20had%20to%20be%20rescued%20by%20security%20personnel%20after%20he%20was%20heckled%20and%20pushed%20by%20the%20protesting%20junior%20doctors%20when%20he%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20inquiry%20committee%20looking%20into%20complaints%20of%20harassment%20and%20intimidation%20on%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Bengal%20assembly%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20asserted%20that%20Pandey%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrongman%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20propagator%20of%20the%20threat%20culture%20in%20state-run%20medical%20colleges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20his%20arrest%20and%20interrogation%2C%20CBI%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20culture%20at%20medical%20colleges%20and%20find%20out%20all%20those%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adhikari%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Ghosh%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20registered%20after%20allegations%20of%20financial%20irregularities%20surfaced.%20The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20had%20handed%20over%20the%20investigation%20to%20the%20CBI%20after%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20registered%20a%20case%20based%20on%20complaints%20filed%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20irregularities%20case%20involves%20irregularities%20in%20award%20of%20contracts%2C%20getting%20the%20infrastructure-related%20tasks%20of%20the%20hospital%20done%20by%20individuals%20or%20firms%20instead%20of%20getting%20them%20done%20by%20the%20state%20public%20works%20department%20(PWD)%2C%20the%20sale%20of%20biomedical%20waste%20which%20is%20illegal%2C%20and%20sale%20of%20selling%20organs%20from%20unidentified%20bodies%20brought%20for%20postmortem%2C%20at%20%26quot%3Blucrative%20prices%26quot%3B%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Ghosh%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20rape-murder%20case%20and%20has%20undergone%20two%20polygraph%20tests.%20%C2%A0He%20and%20the%20police%20officer%20who%20initially%20investigated%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20doctor%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20attempting%20to%20hide%20evidence%20and%20sabotage%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20inside%20the%20seminar%20hall%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20on%20August%209.%20The%20key%20suspect%2C%20civic%20volunteer%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20a%20was%20seen%20on%20CCTV%20during%20investigation%20after%20the%20doctor's%20body%20was%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727977140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Frloqk36c_cbi-generic-650_625x300_19_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-leader-arrested-in-rg-kar-hospital-corruption-case-cbi-6710004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20on%20Thursday%20arrested%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20a%20house-staff%20attached%20to%20R.G.%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20%26amp%3B%20Hospital%2C%20Asish%20Pande%2C%20said%20to%20be%20a%20close%20confidant%20of%20Sandip%20Ghosh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-leader-arrested-in-rg-kar-hospital-corruption-case-cbi-6710004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ladakh%20activist%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20free%2C%20say%20Delhi%20cops%3B%20no%2C%20say%20pleas%20in%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1