nd%20forced%20himself%20on%20me%20and%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20my%20core%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20months%2C%20Roshni%20ran%20away%20and%20returned%20to%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20home.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20time%20later%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20I%20was%20pregnant%20with%20his%20child.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20my%20son.%20I%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20go%20back%20to%20that%20hell%2C%20but%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20his%20house.%20When%20I%20went%20back%2C%20my%20husband%20did%20not%20accept%20me%2C%20as%20I%20had%20been%20away%20for%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20facing%20unimaginable%20challenges%20and%20hardships%2C%20including%20rejection%20by%20her%20own%20family%20and%20societal%20stigma%2C%20Roshni%20refused%20to%20succumb%20to%20despair.%20She%20bravely%20walked%20away%20from%20an%20abusive%20marriage.%20At%2015%2C%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20raising%20a%20newborn%2C%20she%20started%20working%20at%20a%20showroom%2C%20determined%20to%20create%20a%20better%20future%20for%20herself%20and%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2024%2C%20Roshni%20has%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20rural%20girls%20in%20Bihar.%20Driven%20by%20her%20harrowing%20challenges%20and%20personal%20struggles%2C%20she%20has%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20rescuing%20girls%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20trafficking%20and%20preventing%20child%20marriages%20in%20her%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roshni%20has%20successfully%20prevented%20over%2060%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-2-1727791992-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERoshni%20has%20successfully%20prevented%20over%2060%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20survivor%20to%20advocate%3A%20How%20Roshni%20is%20empowering%20young%20girls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Roshni%20joined%20forces%20with%20Childline%20India%20Foundation%2C%20where%20she%20discovered%20a%20community%20of%20women%20who%20shared%20similar%20harrowing%20experiences.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20there%20were%20similar%20women%20like%20me.%20I%20was%20not%20alone.%20I%20thought%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20I%20become%20a%20voice%20for%20such%20women%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20her%20transformation%20from%20a%20survivor%20to%20a%20fierce%20advocate%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20organisations%20such%20as%20Save%20The%20Children%20and%20UNICEF%2C%20she%20spearheaded%20initiatives%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20early%20marriage%20and%20empower%20young%20girls%20to%20reclaim%20their%20futures.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20with%20them%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20prevent%2012%20child%20marriages%20in%20Khagaria%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says