l%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20began%20with%20the%20mandated%2050%20hectares%20in%20Mandvi%20taluka%E2%80%99s%20Karanj%20village%2C%20the%20positive%20impact%20of%20the%20mangroves%20on%20the%20local%20community%20inspired%20further%20expansion%20of%20the%20plantation.%20And%20so%2C%20this%20was%20followed%20by%20another%20100%20hectares%20of%20land%20in%20Hansot%20block%E2%80%99s%20Katpor%20village.%20Both%20projects%20were%20undertaken%20along%20with%20the%20GEC%2C%20the%20nodal%20agency%20for%20such%20activities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mangrove%20plantation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-76-1727772570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368184%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMangrove%20plantation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20estimates%20by%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20there%20is%20a%20potential%20for%20almost%2020%20to%2030%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20being%20sequestered%20per%20hectare%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20economic%20activities%20of%20the%20local%20community%20and%20therefore%2C%20the%20locals%20from%20the%20coastal%20area%20of%20Katpor%20were%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20entire%20process.%20The%20GEC%20collaborated%20with%20a%20local%20community-based%20organisation%2C%20Katpor%20Tamvar%20Vikas%20Samiti%2C%20to%20oversee%20the%20project.%20The%20villagers%20were%20trained%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20mangrove%20planting%2C%20from%20developing%20saplings%20to%20managing%20and%20maintaining%20the%20plantations.%20The%20GEC%20also%20raised%20awareness%20among%20the%20villagers%20about%20the%20environmental%20importance%20of%20mangroves%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20were%20well-equipped%20to%20manage%20and%20maintain%20the%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20five%20to%20six-year%20project%2C%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20workdays%20were%20generated%2C%20providing%20significant%20employment%20opportunities.%20Many%20women%20from%20the%20community%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20various%20processes%20%E2%80%94%20including%20seed%20collection%2C%20manual%20sowing%2C%20nursery%20management%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20contributing%20to%20both%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20and%20their%20own%20economic%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20mangrove%20plantation%2C%20the%20area%20was%20a%20wasteland.%20Farmers%20faced%20a%20tough%20time%20as%20yield%20was%20low%20due%20to%20high%20salinity%20in%20the%20soil%20and%20salty%20winds%20leading%20to%20crop%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rathod.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-77-1727772853.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Babubhai%20Rathod%2C%20former%20sarpanch%20and%20a%20resident%20of%20Karanj.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t