eople%20From%20Drowning%3F%20Ask%20These%20Lifeguards%20in%20Goa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShashikant%20Jadhav%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20lifeguard%20and%20operations%20manager%20with%20Drishti%20Marine%20%E2%80%94%20a%20private%20agency%20tasked%20by%20the%20Goa%20Government%20to%20curb%20incidents%20of%20drowning%20off%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20beaches%20%E2%80%94%20remembers%20what%20inspired%20him%20to%20get%20into%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%E2%80%99m%20from%20Raigad%20district%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20South%20Goa.%20Visiting%20the%20beach%20nearby%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it%20and%20learnt%20how%20to%20swim%20in%20the%20sea%20with%20my%20friends.%20But%20I%20also%20saw%20many%20people%20drowning%20in%20the%20sea%20and%20that%20left%20a%20real%20impression%20on%20me.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20wanted%20a%20job%20where%20I%20could%20save%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Drishti%20Marine%20was%20operational%20in%202008%2C%20Shashikant%20was%20a%20lifeguard%20working%20for%20another%20company%20contracted%20by%20the%20tourism%20department%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267418%2Fgoa-government-school-robotics-coding-scheme-first-india-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoa%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20there%20was%20little%20to%20no%20coordination%20in%20rescue%20efforts.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20the%20people%20in%20charge%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20I%20had%20swam%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20to%20rescue%20someone.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20proper%20equipment%20like%20a%20surfboard%2C%20walkie-talkie%2C%20lifeguard%20jeep%2C%20or%20jet-ski%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20coordination%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20professionalism%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20lack%20of%20beach%20safety%20and%20the%20number%20of%20drowning%20deaths%20Goa%20saw.%20Matters%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202007%20when%20the%20state%20unfortunately%20saw%20200%20people%20drown%20off%20the%20coastline%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20Somani%2C%20founder%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Drishti%20Marine%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20events%20of%202007%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20prompted%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%20and%20put%20together%20an%20efficient%20system%20to%20safeguard%20lives%20along%20beaches.%20One%20of%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20to%20appoint%20a%20professional%20agency%20for%20enhancing%20beach%20safety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drishti%20'Lifesavers'%20(lifeguards)%20saving%20lives%20in%20Goa.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-270x300.jpg%20270w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-768x855.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-150x167.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDrishti%20%E2%80%98Lifesavers%E2%80%99%20(lifeguards)%20saving%20lives%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20was%20tasked%20by%20the%20Goa%20Government%20to%20curb%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171819%2Fdelhi-police-hero-rescue-drowning-child-inspirational%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrowning%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20beaches.%20Once%20it%20was%20awarded%20a%20contract%20to%20offer%20lifeguard%20services%20for%20the%20state%2C%20Shashikant%20was%20among%20the%20first%20lifeguards%20to%20join%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20Drishti%20in%20July%202008%2C%20they%20put%20me%20through%20a%2045-day%20training%20course%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20lifeguarding%20and%20how%20to%20use%20the%20new%20equipment%20given%20to%20us.%20There%20was%20a%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20safety%20here.%20In%20my%20previous%20job%2C%20we%20would%20get%20no%20backup%20during%20rescue%20efforts.%20Now%2C%20whenever%20we%20go%20out%20on%20a%20rescue%2C%20we%20are%20supported%20by%20jet%20skis%2C%20backup%20lifeguards%2C%20etc.%20Also%2C%20we%20receive%20continuous%20training%20and%20have%20reorientation%20sessions%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20methods%20and%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBraving%20the%20waves%3A%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Drishti%20Marine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Drishti%20becoming%20the%20designated%20agency%20to%20provide%20lifeguard%20services%20also%20prompted%20Ashwin%20Ghag%2C%20a%20former%20national-level%20swimmer%2C%20to%20leave%20Pune%20for%20Goa%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%201999%20to%202008%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20swimming%20coach%20for%20children%20in%20Pune%2C%20after%20which%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20senior%20lifeguard.%20Before%20my%20swimming%20coach%20and%20lifeguard%20career%2C%20I%20was%20a%20national-level%20swimmer.%20I%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20father%20to%20become%20a%20lifeguard.%20Watching%20him%20work%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159192%2Fpune-drowning-lives-raju%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20me%20to%20become%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ashwin%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20senior%20lifeguard%20at%20Drishti%20Marine%20currently%20posted%20on%20the%20popular%20and%20crowded%20Calangute%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lifeguards%20-%20Shashikant%20Jadhav%20and%20Ashwin%20Ghag.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashikant%20Jadhav%20and%20Ashwin%20Ghag%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20working%20in%20Pune%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20a%20new%20company%20in%20Goa%20offering%20lifeguarding%20services%20and%20that%20they%20needed%20lifeguards.%20Along%20with%20another%20senior%20lifeguard%20from%20Pune%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Goa.%20Despite%20my%20skills%2C%20I%20had%20little%20experience%20of%20working%20on%20beaches.%20Working%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20in%20swimming%20pools%2C%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20use%20life-saving%20equipment.%20But%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20use%20them%20in%20the%20sea%20due%20to%20my%20lack%20of%20experience%20working%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20Ashwin%20learnt%20after%20joining%20Drishti%20was%20how%20much%20more%20stamina%20a%20lifeguard%20requires%20to%20swim%20into%20a%20massive%20water%20body%20like%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20and%20rescue%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20saving%20someone%20from%20drowning%20in%20a%20swimming%20pool%2C%20you%20are%20working%20in%20a%20confined%20space%20with%20four%20corners%20no%20matter%20its%20size.%20You%20know%20exactly%20where%20to%20jump%20in%2C%20save%20the%20person%20and%20drop%20them%20off%20at%20any%20given%20edge%20of%20the%20pool.%20In%20the%20sea%2C%20you%20can%20only%20save%20someone%20by%20taking%20them%20back%20one%20way.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20confined%20space.%20Another%20thing%20I%20learnt%20about%20were%20rip%20currents%20%E2%80%94%20strong%20and%20narrow%20currents%20that%20can%20pull%20you%20into%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20is%20the%20designated%20first%20responder%20for%20any%20beach-related%20emergency%2C%20including%20cases%20of%20marine%20strandings.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20Rajiv%20claims%20that%20its%20450-plus%20strong%20force%20of%20%E2%80%98lifesavers%E2%80%99%20(lifeguards)%20has%20saved%20about%207%2C700%20people%20from%20drowning%20off%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPatrolling%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20shores%20and%20saving%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeaches%20in%20Goa%20are%20divided%20into%20zones%3A%20swim%20areas%20marked%20by%20red%20and%20yellow%20flags%2C%20no-swim%20zones%20by%20red%20flags%2C%20and%20watersport%20areas%20by%20black-and-white%20flags.%20High-footfall%20beaches%20have%20dedicated%20lifesaver%20towers%20offering%20a%20clear%20vantage%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CSwim%20zones%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20by%20lifesavers%20equipped%20with%20binoculars%2C%20jet%20skis%2C%20spine%20boards%2C%20surfboards%2C%20and%20rescue%20tubes.%20When%20a%20person%20in%20distress%20is%20spotted%20off%20the%20beach%2C%20the%20on-duty%20lifesaver%20notifies%20other%20lifesavers%20via%20radio.%20The%20rescue%20team%20rushes%20to%20assist%20the%20person%20in%20distress%2C%20alerts%20backup%20to%20call%20an%20ambulance%2C%20and%20accompanies%20the%20rescued%20individual%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20evaluation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lifeguards%20along%20the%20Goan%20shoreline%2C%20prepared%20to%20save%20lives.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELifeguards%20along%20the%20Goan%20shoreline%2C%20prepared%20to%20save%20lives.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLifesaver%20towers%20are%20stocked%20with%20emergency%20medical%20equipment%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20first%20aid%20kits%2C%20spine%20boards%2C%20surfboards%2C%20rescue%20boards%2C%20rescue%20tubes%2C%20handheld%20radio%20sets%2C%20bag%20valve%20masks%20to%20assist%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F206387%2Fcpr-first-aid-basic-life-support-cardiopulmonary-resuscitation-mouth-to-mouth-health-care-medical-emergency%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECardiopulmonary%20Resuscitation%20(CPR)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Automated%20External%20Defibrillator%20(A.E.D.)%20machines.%20The%20official%20beach%20jeeps%20are%20on%20standby%20to%20transport%20patients%20or%20distressed%20individuals%20to%20nearby%20health%20facilities%20or%20ambulances.%20Lifesavers%20are%20also%20trained%20in%20first%20aid%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance%20during%20medical%20emergencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20Calangute%20beach%2C%20I%20do%20approximately%2030%20rescues%20a%20month%20because%20there%20is%20always%20a%20large%20crowd%20present%20there.%20Rescues%20usually%20happen%20between%20an%20approximate%20range%20of%2030%20to%2050%20metres%20into%20the%20sea%20%5Bfrom%20the%20shoreline%5D.%20Away%20from%20the%20shoreline%20at%20Calangute%20Beach%2C%20we%20encounter%20a%20lot%20of%20rip%20currents.%20When%20a%20tourist%20encounters%20a%20rip%20current%20by%20swimming%20too%20far%20from%20the%20shore%2C%20they%20panic%20because%20the%20water%20is%20pulling%20them%20into%20the%20sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20the%20heroes%20behind%20the%20rescues%20chosen%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2030%20years%20who%20know%20swimming%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20saving%20victims%20are%20eligible%20to%20become%20Drishti%20lifesavers%2C%20notes%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COur%20hiring%20checklist%20includes%20thorough%20physical%20tests%2C%20interviews%2C%20reference%20checks%2C%20and%20police%20verification.%20The%20physically%20demanding%20nature%20of%20a%20lifesaver%20requires%20that%20men%20and%20women%20who%20apply%20should%20possess%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20physical%20fitness%20and%20our%20training%20team%20does%20the%20rest.%20Every%20lifesaver%20must%20be%20capable%20of%20swimming%20400%20metres%20in%20under%2011%20minutes.%20They%20need%20to%20quickly%20assess%20the%20capabilities%20and%20risks%20of%20individuals%20involved%20in%20aquatic%20activities%2C%20follow%20on-site%20protocols%2C%20and%20provide%20emergency%20medical%20services%20when%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%2C%20%E2%80%9CDrishti%E2%80%99s%20450-strong%20lifesaver%20team%20undergoes%20a%20rigorous%20annual%20refresher%20course%20to%20maintain%20and%20improve%20their%20emergency%20response%20skills%2C%20physical%20fitness%2C%20and%20communication%20abilities.%20The%20training%20includes%20CPR%2C%20first%20aid%2C%20beach%20operations%2C%20jet%20ski%20use%2C%20rescue%20equipment%20handling%2C%20and%20various%20rescue%20techniques.%20In%20addition%20to%20lifesaving%20skills%2C%20they%20also%20receive%20training%20in%20leadership%20and%20soft%20skills%20to%20effectively%20manage%20public%2