0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359465%2Fsustainable-farming-homeschooling-rajesh-mate-smita-dhruvi-diti-mumbai-to-raigad-permaculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrawing%20on%20tradition%20and%20his%20knowledge%20of%20permaculture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20founded%20%E2%80%98Tieedi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%98Take%20It%20Easy%2C%20Easy%20Does%20It%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMission%20Green%20Mile%3A%20A%20step%20towards%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20very%20personal%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20natural%20buildings%20on%20my%20own%20and%20grow%20my%20own%20food.%20But%20when%20we%20started%20clearing%20the%20undergrowth%2C%20we%20began%20to%20experience%20firsthand%20the%20problem%20of%20plastic%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20informs%20me%20as%20we%20sit%20in%20one%20of%20his%20mud%20houses%2C%20sipping%20fresh%20Darjeeling%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20compound%20has%20since%20transformed%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353885%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-homestay-mussoorie-uttarakhand-aseem-neetu-varma-sistainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20eco-resort%20with%20its%20own%20waste%20segregation%20and%20composting%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20features%20a%20few%20cottages%20built%20from%20mud%20and%20bamboo%2C%20where%20guests%20often%20visit%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20various%20initiatives%20Tieedi%20has%20undertaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtsow%2C%20who%20spent%20his%20formative%20years%20in%20Kurseong%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20municipality%20about%2040%20km%20away%20from%20Darjeeling%20%E2%80%94%20says%20that%20the%20transformation%20he%20witnessed%20over%20the%20years%20pushed%20him%20further%20to%20explore%20ways%20in%20which%20sustainability%20and%20development%20could%20coexist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%