nk%5C%22%3Eher%20videos%20began%20going%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20laughed%20at%20me%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varsha%20shared.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20something%20incredible%20happened.%20My%20videos%20started%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20people%20were%20following%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20talent%20and%20charm%20earned%20her%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20popular%20dance%20reality%20show%20%3Cem%3EDance%20Deewane%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20she%20wowed%20both%20the%20judges%20and%20the%20audience.%20One%20of%20the%20judges%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20a%20real%20hero.%20People%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20you.%20You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20life%20drown%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20fought%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20emotional%20moment%20on%20the%20show%2C%20she%20reflected%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20dream%20about%20this%2C%20but%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20happen.%20Life%20has%20a%20funny%20way%20of%20giving%20you%20a%20second%20chance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%205.8%20million%20followers%2C%20Varsha%20is%20living%20proof%20that%20an%20undying%20passion%20can%20take%20you%20to%20places%20you%20never%20even%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727446429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20into%20poverty%2C%20Varsha%20Solanki%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%20while%20nurturing%20a%20lifelong%20passion%20for%20dance.%20After%20marriage%20and%20motherhood%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20to%20rekindle%20her%20art%2C%20going%20viral%20and%20reaching%20five%20million%20followers.%20Here's%20her%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367863%2Fvarsha-solanki-socia